---
/**
 * Fallback for unknown MDX tags.
 *
 * When an MDX file uses a capitalised tag that isn't registered in
 * mdx-components.ts (e.g. a typo like <Foobar>), the Proxy in
 * mdx-components.ts returns this component instead of undefined.
 * It renders only the slot children, effectively stripping the unknown
 * tag and leaving the inner content as plain text/HTML.
 *
 * This is intentionally a no-op wrapper — do not add markup or styles.
 */
---

<slot />
